{
  "id": "adv_love_2305_03_01",
  "title": "Episode 3 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――高校三年生　七月　学校",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Third year of high sch‚ July‚\nat school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "「先生になりたい」と答える",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh004.m4a",
              "text": "なんとなく先生に\nなりたいなとは思っているよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I guess I've sort of thought about\nbecoming a teacher.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 51.1252552589,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "「ない」と答える",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh005.m4a",
              "text": "特にないな\n先生か……考えたことなかったな",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Not particularly. Being a teacher…\nnever really crossed my mind.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 55.2212185939,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "息抜きに誘う",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "この後、時間ある？\nたまには息抜きしにどこかに出掛けない？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Do you have time later?\nWant to take a break\nand go somewhere?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 135.7593986512,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei010.m4a",
              "text": "いいわよ。ちょうど私も\nどこか行きたいなって思っていたの",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Sounds good. I was actually thinking\nI'd like to go somewhere too.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 140.7845676423,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 7182.100041500007
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 6966.666666700007
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 146.451234309
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_coast-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 147.751234309
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei011.m4a",
              "text": "うわぁ……綺麗……！\n夕日が水面に反射してキラキラしてる！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Wow… it's so beautiful!\nThe sunset reflecting\non the water is sparkling!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 149.2845717114,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "喜んでくれて良かった\n少し海岸を散歩しようか",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm glad you're enjoying it.\nShall we take a little walk\nalong the beach?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 157.751238378,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei012.m4a",
              "text": "ええ。今まで夏はずっとダンスの\n合宿だったから。こうやって\n夏っぽいことするのは久しぶりだわ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yes‚ please. I've spent every summer\nat dance camps‚\nso it's been a while since\nI've done something summer like this.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 162.3899446806,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "ダンス漬けの人生だったんだな\nそういえば、最近ダンスの方はどうなんだ？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "So‚ your life has been\nall about dance‚ huh?\nBy the way‚\nhow's the dancing going lately?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 172.0232759794,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei013.m4a",
              "text": "八月にあるダンス大会に向けて練習している\nところよ。コーチに褒められる\n回数も増えてきて、調子がいいの",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm practicing for the dance\ncompetition in August.\nGetting more credits from the coach‚\nand feeling good about it.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 178.3034570059,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei014.m4a",
              "text": "このまま宣言通り、勉強もダンスも頑張って\nお父さんに認めてもらうわ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm going to work hard in both\nstudying and dancing as I declared‚\nand make my father acknowledge me.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 188.0034570059,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "俺も応援してる。きっとお父さんも\n怜の頑張りを認めてくれるよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I'm rooting for you too.\nI'm sure your dad\nwill acknowledge your efforts.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 194.8034570059,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei015.m4a",
              "text": "そうだと……いいな……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I hope… so…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 200.0063727697,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "模試の復習をする",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "今から復習をしよう\nまたすぐ次の模試があるし\n傾向と対策は大切だ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Let's review now.\nThere's another mock exam coming up\nsoon‚ and understanding the trends\nand strategies is important.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 203.3063636144,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rei",
              "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
              "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei016.m4a",
              "text": "そうよね、まだB判定だし……頑張るわ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "You're right.\nI'm still aiming for a B grade…\nI'll do my best…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 209.1469756444,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.6333334049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺達は来週行われる\n七月の全国模試に向けて勉強に励んでいた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We've been studying hard for the\nnational mock exams next week.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4333334049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ここはXをYに代入してそのまま――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ substituting X for Y‚\nlike this――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3805886349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.2286610207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとだ、解けた……\n少しずつだけど、公式の使い方が\n分かってきた気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I got it… I solved it!\nI feel like I'm starting to understand\nhow to use the formulas bit by bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2286610207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "理解が早いね\nこれだったら次の模試で\nB判定も狙えるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You catch on fast. With this‚\nyou might be able to aim for a\nB grade on the next mock exam.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2286606392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.9252583107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}の\n教え方が上手だからよ\n先生なんかより全然分かりやすいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚\nyou're good at teaching.\nYour explanations are way easier\nto understand than the teacher's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9252583107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "今まで勉強に楽しさなんて\n感じたことなかったけれど\n少しずつ楽しくなってきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never really found studying\nenjoyable before‚ but little by little‚\nit's starting to be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8919239601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2585885923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}は夢とかないの？\n先生とか向いてると思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you have any dreams‚\n{user}?\nI think you'd make a great teacher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2585885923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1632820209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、怜みたいに\nこれがやりたいっていう信念が\nある訳ではないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ like Rei‚\nI don't have a clear conviction\nabout what I want to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1632820209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.2244608005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなまっすぐな怜を\n本当にカッコいいと思っているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really admire someone as\nstraightforward as you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2244608005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 70.1343390545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと……\nそんなまっすぐ見つめて言わないでよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait…\nPlease don't look right at me …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9663031658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.0996364992
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.0996364992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2305_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん\n思ったことをそのまま\n言っただけなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry. I just said what I was thinking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0996364992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.1168172758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
